理財規劃與實務課程大綱







請「遵守智慧財產權觀念」及「不得不法影印或網路非法下載」Please respect intellectual property rights and do not illegally copy or print materials.









理財規劃與實務課程大綱




課程介紹（Course Description）：
 
              
			  全球經濟成長已有趨緩的情形，加上臺灣M型社會也愈來愈顯著，如何運用各項投資工具（股票、債券、基金、期貨、選擇權、外匯、黃金）與投資分析（基本分析與技術分析），以獲取合理的報酬將是一門不可或缺的理財課題程。本課程的主要目標為讓學員們瞭解理財的基本原理與工具，協助跨出個人理財成功的第一步。課程內容兼具公司財報分析能力的培養以及投資人選股能力的提升，參與課程之學員將可以利用做中學習，體驗理論知識與交易實務之間的落差，進而對財富管理有更深入之理解，做出正確的投資決策。

        Slowdown in global economic growth have scenarios, plus Taiwan－m society has become more and more significant, how to use various investment instruments (stocks, bonds, mutual funds, futures, options, foreign exchange, gold) and investment analysis (fundamental analysis and technical analysis) to obtain reasonable compensation is an essential topic as financial management process.The main objective of this course is for students who understand financial management principles and tools to help out a financial success of the first step. Course content combines analysis of earnings ability of candidate ability and investment promotion, participation retrainees will be able to use learning experience gap between theoretical knowledge and trade practices, and wealth management have a better understanding of, and make the right investment decisions. 
			  			  
              






